The Official Nexus 7 Dock is designed with a rubberized bottom and weighted down to provide the best docking performance.  Pogo-pins charges the Nexus 7 and provides sound to the audio jack which is ideal for powered speaker systems. With the official ASUS Nexus 7 Dock, there is no need to physically connect to the Nexus 7's USB port because pogo-pins do all the work, allowing rapid docking and undocking.
